stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Started: Lambda invoked

    Started --> Completed: All chunks processed successfully
    Started --> Failed: Unrecoverable error
    Started --> Partial: Some chunks failed

    Partial --> Completed: Retry succeeds
    Partial --> Failed: Max retries exceeded

    Completed --> [*]: Notification sent
    Failed --> [*]: Error notification sent

    state Started {
        [*] --> Scraping: run_type = scraper
        [*] --> Ingesting: run_type = ingestion
        [*] --> Analyzing: run_type = analysis

        Scraping --> SQS_Enqueue: New content found
        Ingesting --> Relevance_Check: Haiku scoring
        Relevance_Check --> SQS_Enqueue: Score above threshold
        Relevance_Check --> Skipped: Below threshold
        Analyzing --> Gap_Extraction: Sonnet analysis
        Gap_Extraction --> DB_Write: Gaps + Regulations saved
    }

    note right of Completed
        Pipeline stats recorded:
        - regulations_added
        - gaps_added
        - duration_seconds
        - errors_count
    end note
